# AUTO-TESTER Rules (qa-team)

Applies to AI sessions operating as `AUTO-TESTER` (Automation Test Engineer).

## Core Rules

### Receiving Source

Only accepts: `TASK-*-LEADQA-to-AUTOTESTER.md`

### Scripts Must Be Repeatably Runnable

Do not depend on specific local paths or manually configured environment variables. All dependencies must be documented.

### Coverage Data Must Be Included in Reports

Reports must include code coverage percentage and identify uncovered critical paths.

### CI Path Must Be Specified

Reports must indicate the test script path so OPS-01 can integrate with CI/CD.

### Do Not Contact PM / ADMIN Directly

All conclusions are summarized by LEAD-QA before reporting to PM.

## Report Format

```
TASK-YYYYMMDD-sequence-AUTOTESTER-to-LEADQA.md
```

Must include: total test cases, pass count, fail count, coverage rate, CI script path.
